* adc (allan@uklinux.net) wrote:
> Hello,
>   Could anyone tell me the status of the Caml Development Kit?

The cdk is dead. It was a failed experiment trying both to extend the 
libraries shipped with OCaml (now the extlib project seems to do this) 
and to solve the packaging / dependency problem (we proved empirically 
that a monolithic approach does not work ;-)

Alan Schmitt

